    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine... <persName key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke" ref="#people/3001"
                            >Riccardus</persName> et <persName key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke"
                            ref="#people/3002">Iordanes</persName>... <rs key="#Princeps"
                            >principes</rs>... …fidelium... universitas noverit quam <persName
                            key="#Count #childOf" ref="#people/5039">adenulfus</persName> et
                            <persName key="#Count #childOf" ref="#people/5063">landulfus</persName>
                        et <persName key="#Count #childOf" ref="#people/5064">paldolfus</persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/5065">landoni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs> aquinensis cum toti alii <rs key="#Count"
                            >comites</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/2795">aquini</placeName> contra animam
                        nostram cogitaverunt ac inimicos nostros intra nostram provinciam
                        invitaverunt unde secundum longobardorum legem <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Inflow #Confiscation #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            >omnes ipsorum res nostro fisco deducte sunt</rs>... Nunc autem <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per interventum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory" ref="#people/4201">landulfi filii
                            auloaldi</persName> et <persName key="#Intercessory" ref="#people/4200"
                            >paldulfi filii Guale</persName>. damus atque concedimus tibi <persName
                            key="#Count #childOf" ref="#people/5066">iohanni <rs key="#Count"
                                >comiti</rs> qui clamatur scinto</persName> et <rs key="#childOf"
                            >filio</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count #fidelisOf" ref="#people/5067">landolfi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs> nostro dilecto <rs key="#fidelisOf"
                            >fideli</rs>. hoc est <rs key="#Castle">castellum</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Castle"
                            ref="#places/5149">sancti iohannis in carreca</placeName> per has
                        denique <rs key="#Fines">fines</rs>... [<foreign>segue la descrizione dei
                            confini</foreign>] totum et integrum per suprascriptas fines et cum
                        universis suis pertinentiis. <rs key="#Profits_of_justice">iudicalia</rs>.
                            <rs key="#Property_of_persons_without_heirs">excaditiones</rs> de
                        homines qui ibidem residentes sunt vel fuerunt necnon et omnia alia <rs
                            key="#Servitium">servitia</rs> que iuste suis senoribus facere soliti
                        sunt... Ex iussione prefate serenissime potestatis scriptum per manus
                            <persName key="#Writer #Judge" ref="#people/3064">iohannis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> in anno octavo principatus ipsius Riccardi et
                        domini Iordanis... et tertio anno <rs key="#Marquis/duke #Marca/ducatum"
                            >ducatus</rs> illorum <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/2343"
                                ><geogName key="#Cities #Marca/ducatum" ref="#estates/3001"
                                >caiete</geogName></placeName>. Datum octabo idus iulii anno ab
                        incarnatione d. n. Ihesu Christi M sexagesimo sexto indictione tertia. </ab>
                </div>
